browser js

javascript can only be run in the browser.
It is basically used on the client side
We can add html tags
javascript can run in any browser engine 
It is used in front end developement



node js

node js can be run out of the browser.
It is mostly used on the server side.
We cant add html tags.
node js can run only with v8 engine of google chrome
It is used in back end developement
